<h2>View and filter work items</h2>

<p>The work reporting page provides a comprehensive view of all work items, with powerful filtering and search capabilities to help you find and manage work items.</p>

<h3>Accessing the work items page</h3>
<p>Navigate to <strong>Reporting → Work reporting</strong> from the main navigation menu.</p>

<h3>Using filters</h3>
<p>The left sidebar provides multiple filter options:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Search:</strong> Search by work item title or work item code</li>
    <li><strong>RAG Status:</strong> Filter by Green, Amber-Green, Amber, Amber-Red, or Red</li>
    <li><strong>Business Area:</strong> Filter by business area/portfolio</li>
    <li><strong>Phase:</strong> Filter by work item phase</li>
    <li><strong>Flagship:</strong> Show only flagship work items</li>
    <li><strong>Priority:</strong> Filter by work item priority</li>
</ul>
<p>Filters can be combined - for example, you can search for "amber" work items in a specific business area.</p>

<h3>Work items table</h3>
<p>The main table displays:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Title:</strong> Work item name (click to view details)</li>
    <li><strong>Code:</strong> Work item code (e.g., DEL-DDT-001)</li>
    <li><strong>RAG Status:</strong> Current status with colour coding</li>
    <li><strong>Business Area:</strong> Associated business area</li>
    <li><strong>Phase:</strong> Current work item phase</li>
    <li><strong>Priority:</strong> Work item priority</li>
</ul>

<h3>Sorting</h3>
<p>Click on any column header to sort the table. Click again to reverse the sort order. Sortable columns include:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Title</li>
    <li>Code</li>
    <li>RAG Status</li>
    <li>Business Area</li>
    <li>Phase</li>
    <li>Priority</li>
</ul>

<h3>Pagination</h3>
<p>If there are many work items, they are displayed across multiple pages. Use the pagination controls at the bottom to navigate between pages.</p>

<h3>Viewing work item details</h3>
<p>Click on any work item title to view the full work item details page, which includes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Overview information</li>
    <li>Milestones, updates and successes</li>
    <li>RAG tracking history</li>
    <li>Team members</li>
    <li>Contacts and governance</li>
    <li>Strategic alignment</li>
    <li>And much more</li>
</ul>

<h3>Creating new work items</h3>
<p>If you have admin permissions, you'll see a <strong>Create entry</strong> button in the top right. This allows you to create a new work item.</p>

<h3>Tips for effective filtering</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Use search to quickly find work items by name or code</li>
    <li>Combine RAG status with business area to focus on specific areas</li>
    <li>Filter by phase to see work items at similar stages</li>
    <li>Use flagship filter to focus on high-priority work items</li>
    <li>Clear filters by removing selections or refreshing the page</li>
</ul>

